      <!-- Card 1 - Left -->
      <div class="scrapbook-card card-left">
        <div class="card-inner">
          <p class="card-text">It all began in college. We were both part of the dance society — Suhani as the Vice President and Mitanshi as the Creative Head.</p>
          <div class="card-images large-images">
            <img loading="lazy" src="{{ '1.1.jpg' | asset_url }}" alt="College days">
            <img loading="lazy" src="{{ '1.2.JPG' | asset_url }}" alt="Dance society">
